{"tid":1168980,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本亞馬遜停售華為產品","createTime":"2019-05-24T05:17:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-24T07:19:36.000Z","uid":39464,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"eb47625ee3281cb8bbcc99cb3291d1bd8a20a345","tid":1168980,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T05:17:04.000Z","msg":"據《日本經濟新聞》，因美國對華為的出口禁令，亞馬遜日本（Amazon Japan）已停止直銷華為產品。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，現時在亞馬遜日本專門銷售華為產品的網頁已無法進行購買，平板電腦和個人電腦等幾乎所有華為産品都標注為「無庫存」，且沒重新補貨計劃。産品説明欄中則顯示，「本產品發生了操作系統（OS）等方面的重大風險」，很有可能是由於美國Google軟件可能無法在華為產品上使用而停止直銷。<br />\n<br />\n亞馬遜日本回應稱，此舉是「為了讓用戶能安心購物，正在討論應對舉措」。華為還在日本樂天購物網站「樂天市場」設有網店。樂天則表示，「目前針對相關店舖沒有調整計劃」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1558672525874&amp;issue=20190524\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1558672525874%26issue%3D20190524&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=f6c57eb6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Ffin%2Finstantf2.php%3Fnode%3D1558672525874%26issue%3D20190524&h=3a816121\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/fin/instantf2.php?node=1558672525874&amp;issue=20190524</a>"},{"pid":"3d00736eb6d9b9fc34ab604dfd15f39fb03f20f1","tid":1168980,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T05:29:39.000Z","msg":"本製品はOS（オペレーションシステム）等についての懸念が発生しています。本製品に関するお問い合わせはメーカーコールセンターまでお問い合わせ下さい。<br />\nHUAWEIお客様サポート 0120-798-288 【フリーダイヤル】受付時間:9:00～20:00(年中無休) <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d5dfbefef8fd85fa6bae610531c0fdd0f24266d","tid":1168980,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T05:30:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.amazon.co.jp/huawei?channel=afterservice\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.co.jp%2Fhuawei%3Fchannel%3Dafterservice&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhEcTp%2BQsjpNju1TtMRGBB4E%3D&h=441aa489\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amazon.co.jp/huawei?channel=afterservice</a>"},{"pid":"0cde4b5d204e97e8a2c5be251e3969c07c257718","tid":1168980,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T05:32:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23496714183f8ffdbd67d6bb86842906029f1af7","tid":1168980,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T06:03:44.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"143923a2433e32955daa5da149c4bf5bdf029985","tid":1168980,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T06:43:41.000Z","msg":"日本Amazon仲賣緊好多淘寶貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"457f506ef180a7874f7a2f1457823b5bf41083f3","tid":1168980,"uid":220382,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-24T07:19:36.000Z","msg":"有錢都唔會買<br />\n仲賣黎做咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}